## Mission: Support small business owners

## The problem: It is expensive and complicated to start and sustain a small business.

## ##
## Requirements ##
# It should be easier to set up a small business
# Taxes should be easier to understand and file
# Insurance should cost less
# Small businesses are also consumers. Consumer protection is critical for owners, employees, and customers.
## ##

### Policy Recommendations: ###
# Tax code should be less complicated and cost less (see also Tax Code Policy)
# Individual and group insurance for small business owners should have more options and they should be cheaper and more options. 
    # They should be able to opt in themselves and employees to programs like Medicaid (See also healthcare priorities).


### Budget ###
# Budget unknown

### Measure Success ###
# Average cost of tax preparation services across all businesses
# Average insurance costs
